text: Hello. There?
Hi there. I have been seeing those St Judes commercials lately.
That's nice. Have you ever donated to any charity?
Yes I have I have never given money though because I'm broke lol. I give blood regularly. What about yourself?
I regularly donate some money or things to children's charity
That's awesome! I hate seeing kids going through that stuff. Its terrible.
Yes. But we have to help them to support their lives

Very true! Ever since I had my daughter It really saddens me to see kids hurting. The charity does such great work though. We have a children's hospital where I live and there is a guy that dresses up like batman for the kids..
Haha. So the kids will enjoy seeing him.  And i too see some people who helps the children and children's charity everyday
He has the full get up. Bat mobile and everything. Do you have kids?
I have two sons. They are married. What is your daughter doing.?
Oh nice I always wanted a son. My daughter is in the living room reading. She is six.
That's nice. You always make her to help some children and children's charity.
Do you have any grand kids?
Yes. I have. They have helping tendency.
How do they help you?
They help for children's charity.
Oh that's amazing! I need to get mine to do more things like that. What do they do to help? Maybe I can get mine to do the same.
You try to help someone through website. But be aware, there might be some fraudulent
I am sure there are some frauds out there. Well that's good that they help. My daughter is in girl scouts and they called the bingo numbers for a nursing home.
